<i>noun</i>: 엄중 [엄중], 엄정 [엄정], 엄밀성 [엄밀썽] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>엄중 [엄중]</dt><br>
<dd>1. strictness; severity</dd><br>
<dd>매우 엄함.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of being very strict.</dd><br>
<dd>2. strictness; sternness</dd><br>
<dd>엄격하고 정중함.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of being strict yet polite.</dd><br>
<dt>엄정 [엄정]</dt><br>
<dd>1. strictness; rigidness</dd><br>
<dd>엄격하고 바름.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being strict and right.</dd><br>
<dd>2. fairness; impartiality</dd><br>
<dd>날카롭고 공정함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being sharp and fair.</dd><br>
<dt>엄밀성 [엄밀썽]</dt><br>
<dd>strictness; preciseness; closeness</dd><br>
<dd>빈틈이나 잘못이 전혀 없을 만큼 엄격하고 세밀한 성질.</dd><br>
<dd>A quality of being strict and minute without any loopholes or errors.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>